             was indicted for <rs id="t18210718-93-off540" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18210718-93-off540" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18210718-93-off540" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18210718-93-cd541" type="crimeDate">29th of June</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18210718-93-off540 t18210718-93-cd541"></join>, one knapsack, value 6 d.; three shirts, value 6 s.; one pair of shoes, value 6 d.; one pair of boots, value 2 s.; four brushes, value 1 s.; one knife, value 2 d.; one sovereign, and 8 s. in monies numbered
            </rs>, the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18210718-93-victim873" type="victimName">
                     John 
                     Wilson
                  <interp inst="t18210718-93-victim873" type="surname" value="Wilson"></interp>
